title: Second Date Update UPDATE: Drive-By Egging
itunes:title: Second Date Update UPDATE: Drive-By Egging
description: About a year ago, two of our listeners went on an unconventional Halloween-themed date and came to us for a Second Date Update...And they've been together ever since! They've even started a new annual tradition because of it, and are back on the show to tell us what it is and how they've been doing!
